2 the department of justice, fish and game warden, park ranger, or other public safety officer with arrest authority,
3 employed by a state, local, or state-based tribal authority and certified by the public safety officer standards and
4 training council; or
5 (b) a sheriff.
6 (7) "MAXIMUM MEDICAL IMPROVEMENT" HAS THE SAME MEANING AS PROVIDED IN 39-71-116.
7 (8) "PERMANENT TOTAL DISABILITY" HAS THE SAME MEANING AS PROVIDED IN 39-71-116."
